        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field-note">The image file is stored in Supabase, and MongoDB only keeps the resulting photo URL.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="submit-panel">
    <div class="submit-copy">
      <div>
        <h3>Ready to send the report?</h3>
        <p>Check that your contact number, severity, and location are correct. The system will try to refresh GPS again before final submission.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="required-pill">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"/></svg>
        Required fields only
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="submit-btn" type="button" onclick="submitReport()">
      <!-- Heroicon: paper-airplane -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 12 3.269 3.125A59.769 59.769 0 0 1 21.485 12 59.768 59.768 0 0 1 3.27 20.875L5.999 12Zm0 0h7.5"/></svg>
      Submit Emergency Report
    </button>
  </div>
  </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="report-map-panel dashboard-map-panel">
    <div class="dashboard-map-shell">
      <div class="gps-map-wrap" id="gpsMapWrap">
        <div class="gps-map-head">
          <span id="gpsMapLabel">Mapandan, Pangasinan overview</span>
          <a id="gpsMapLink" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open map</a>
        </div>
        <div class="gps-map-canvas">
          <iframe class="gps-map-frame" id="gpsMapFrame" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
          <div class="gps-map-view-toggle">
            <button class="gps-map-control" id="gpsMapViewToggle" type="button" disabled title="Switch between standard and satellite imagery">
              Show satellite image
            </button>
